OL,3,CPolice investigate after man dies at
OL,4,CCardiff recycling site
OL,6,FPolice have launched an investigation
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a man at a
OL,8,Frecycling site in Cardiff.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,Freports of an injured man at the
OL,12,FAtlantic Recycling site in the Rumney
OL,13,Farea of the city on Monday afternoon
OL,14,F(July 8).
OL,16,FThe man involved in the incident was a
OL,17,Fcontractor carrying out maintenance at
OL,18,Fthe site.
OL,20,FSouth Wales Police said the man's
OL,21,Ffamily has been informed.
