OL,6,FA spokesperson for the force added:
OL,7,F"The Health and Safety Executive has
OL,8,Falso been informed and an
OL,9,Finvestigation into the incident is
OL,10,Fongoing."
OL,12,FA spokesperson from Dauson
OL,13,FEnvironmental Group said: "Dauson
OL,14,FEnvironmental Group can confirm an
OL,15,Fincident occurred on Monday 8th July
OL,16,F2024 involving a contractor carrying
OL,17,Fout maintenance at the Atlantic
OL,18,FRecycling site in Cardiff.
